caption:
Service connects us, reminding each and every one of us that kindness and empathy is a universal language. In serving others, we often times find our greatest purpose.
☀️
Yesterday United Solar had the honor and opportunity to connect through service. Yesterday United gathered at Feed My Starving Child in Tempe, AZ to volunteer in ending childhood hunger. We contributed to a grand total of 63,504 meals for children around the globe.
☀️
